	"Compile the receiver as a regex matcher. May raise RxParser>>syntaxErrorSignal	or RxParser>>compilationErrorSignal.	This is a part of the Regular Expression Matcher package, (c) 1996, 1999 Vassili Bykov.	Refer to `documentation' protocol of RxParser class for details."
^ RxParser preferredMatcherClass for: (RxParser new parse: self) ignoreCase: true
]

